entries.femaleVariant: Hear me, people! Haiti was a warning of what's to come!
Turn from your screens! Abandon your vices!
Those in the towers and clouds see you as blind! They will watch idly as you drown!
A single finger can be broken, but all together they form a fist!
We must join hands! We must be strong! Before it is too late!
The great wave that will cleanse our world is coming!
